description: A very special "one of a kind" Mid-Century Oasis, and former home to several A-List celebrities. Nestled in a small cul de sac just 2.5 minutes behind The Beverly Hills Hotel, close to Sunset Blvd. This home has an incredible "vibe" , featuring an open floor-plan with excellent indoor/ outdoor flow and tons of natural light,  9 sky-lights, plus 3 oversized fireplaces. Large sumptuous Primary Suite w/  luxuriously appointed bath, plus 2nd bedroom both feature walls of glass which open out to a dramatic 50 ft. Waterfall, pond, lush yard & Fire Pit, with trails leading to hilltop Yoga area.  Updated newer Kitchen w/ porcelain counters, custom cabinetry, & top of the line MIELE appliances. Spacious, light-filled living & dining area set atop the trees. Downstairs features a private 3rd bedroom w/ separate gated entrance, perfect for guests, teenager, office or live-in. Media Den with Bar and fantastic sunken "conversation pit", around a fireplace, perfect for movie nights or friendship circles. Heated pool with new equipment glows from every room at night. Private and Tranquil with only 2 homes on street and ample parking rarely found in the hills. Private, walled and gated entry, ready to move in! This gem is an incomparable property and rare offering.
